#

Syrniki (Cheese Pancakes)

25 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGlutenEggs

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastEasySweet

Description

Deliciously fluffy cheese pancakes, perfect for a sweet breakfast or snack.

Ingredients

  • cottage cheese: 1 cup
  • eggs: 1
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • flour: 1/2 cup
  • baking powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1/4 teaspoon
  • oil or butter (for frying): 3 tablespoons
